MassRetainagePaymentAdjust is a BusinessTask
    owned by ap

    Patterns
        implements ManualTransaction
        implements StaticJava
            Reports
                MassRetainagePaymentAdjustReport

    Parameters
        ContractGroup

        Contract
        	context of ContractGroup


        ContractLine
            context of ContractGroup
        Company                 is a PayablesCompany

        PurchaseOrder



        PurchaseOrderLine
        ReportOption            is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                SplitPayment   value is "1"
                RemoveFromHold value is "2"
        NewPercent              is Decimal size 7.3
        PaymentDate             is Date
        PayInvImmed             is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Yes value is "Y"
                No  value is "N"
        PrintPayDtl             is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Yes value is "Y"
                No  value is "N"
        Update                  is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                Yes value is "Y"
                No  value is "N"

    Parameter Rules
        ReportOption
        	initial value is "1"
            default to "1"
        NewPercent
            constraint (NewPercent >= 000000 and NewPercent <= 100000)
                "<NewPercent>ValueNotInRange"
        PayInvImmed
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        PrintPayDtl
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"
        Update
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"

    Actions
        MassRetainagePaymentAdjust is a Set Action
            allow unlimited concurrency
